Since The Ntegrator married deal came along at $0.0118  Ntegrator dump out at open market all the way til $0.005/$0.006 before they started to form the base.Many retailers were taken aback and caught out by this crazy play as most would have bought $0.011  $0.010  $0.009 and then flushed out later at $0.005 to $0.006.ArionEnt as a counter have no little risk of going concern as they are almost a shell IMO having revenues of less than $1mil for the past FYs  cash of over $2 mil and a total liability of only $580k.Hence  it baffles why Ntegrator bought shares at $0.0118 to dump open market but I guess this is syndicated move to load up cheap.$0.005 almost impossible to get  $0.006 is possible but not easy. Sellers have almost dried at $0.006.Based on the weekly chart  $0.005-$0.006 have proven to be an incredible support and almost unlikely to be broken.For me  $0.006 I will collect as I do not see downside but have to hold. I believe it is just a matter of time we see some catalyst for pump.
